<HEADLINE>
<P>
OBITUARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Back, Annie T., 77, of Sunland, homemaker. Forest Lawn Mortuary, Hollywood 
Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Calkins, Erling, 77, of Glendale, retired minister for Seventh-day Adventist 
Church.Forest Lawn Mortuary, Glendale.  
