<HEADLINE>
<P>
GIRLS' ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In other Buena tournament games: 
</P>
<P>
 Alemany 75, Santa Clara 18 -- Kelly McKay scored 17 of her 25 points in the 
first quarter as the Indians (2-0) routed the Saints (1-2). 
</P>
<P>
 Teammate Carly Funicello scored 12 points, while Kelli Kobayashi added 11 for 
Alemany, ranked second in the state. 
</P>
<P>
 Buena 81, Chatsworth 33 -- Ashley Jackson came off the bench to score 13 
points for the Bulldogs (1-0). 
